 \frac{2 u^2}{u^2-4} = 2+\frac{8}{u^2-4} = \frac{2(u^2-4)+8}{u^2-4} ? 
\frac{2u^2}{u^2-4} = 2\left[ \frac{u^2}{u^2-4} \right] = 2\left[ \frac{u^2-4+4}{u^2-4} \right] = 2\left[ 1 + \frac{4}{u^2-4} \right] = 2 + \frac{8}{u^2-4}
